OL,3,CJersey's Government to introduce
OL,4,Cmodern slavery legislation
OL,6,FJersey's government has confirmed it
OL,7,Fintends to introduce modern slavery
OL,8,Flegislation to the island.
OL,10,FIt comes after a landmark ruling on
OL,11,FThursday 5 February, where the
OL,12,Fisland's longest serving politician,
OL,13,FDeputy Philip Ozouf, was given 120
OL,14,Fhours of community service for
OL,15,Fbreaking immigration laws.
OL,17,FThe Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,18,FFarnham, says: "Jersey must always
OL,19,Fprotect the most vulnerable people in
OL,20,Four community.
