OL,3,CJersey's Government to introduce
OL,4,Cmodern slavery legislation
OL,6,F"Bringing in modern slavery
OL,7,Flegislation will strengthen our laws,
OL,8,Fhelp stop exploitation and make sure
OL,9,Fvictims get the help and support they
OL,10,Fneed."
OL,12,FThe proposed reforms will focus on
OL,13,Fpreventing exploitation, improving
OL,14,Fsupport and protection for victims,
OL,15,Fand ensuring the authorities have
OL,16,Fclear powers, safeguards and
OL,17,Faccountability to tackle modern
OL,18,Fslavery effectively.
