OL,3,CJersey's Government to introduce
OL,4,Cmodern slavery legislation
OL,6,F"This legislation will give
OL,7,Fenforcement agencies clearer powers
OL,8,Fand stronger protection for people at
OL,9,Frisk.
OL,11,F"By listening to frontline services,
OL,12,Femployers and those with lived
OL,13,Fexperience, we will design a modern
OL,14,Flegal framework that reflects best
OL,15,Fpractice and provides clear, practical
OL,16,Fprotection against exploitation for
OL,17,Feveryone in our community.
